Hybrid Architecture Design
text
User Query → Query Router → Persona LoRA (weights) → Response in Holly voice
                           → ChromaDB RAG (vectors) → Facts → Persona LoRA → Facts in Holly voice
Weights (Soul): Persona, concepts, spiritual, rlhf, SHP at reduced scale. Small, handcrafted adapters that define voice and core identity.

Vectors (Brain): All factual domain knowledge in ChromaDB with sentence-transformer embeddings. Single unified collection with metadata for domain filtering.

Router (Judgment): Keyword-based classifier. Factual queries ("what is", "explain", "history of") route to RAG. Conversational queries route to persona. Default: try RAG, fall back to persona.

